        "content": "<p>In the following example, the widget only displays in one place:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">ProofWidgets.Component.HtmlDisplay</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">open</span> <span class=\"n\">Lean</span> <span class=\"n\">ProofWidgets</span> <span class=\"n\">Jsx</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">syntax</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"foo\"</span> <span class=\"n\">term</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">term</span>\n<span class=\"n\">elab_rules</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">term</span>\n<span class=\"bp\">|</span> <span class=\"bp\">`</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">term</span><span class=\"bp\">|</span> <span class=\"n\">foo</span><span class=\"bp\">%$</span><span class=\"n\">stx</span> <span class=\"bp\">$</span><span class=\"n\">t</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"k\">do</span>\n  <span class=\"k\">let</span> <span class=\"n\">ht</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"bp\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">h2</span><span class=\"bp\">&gt;</span><span class=\"n\">Hello</span> <span class=\"n\">world</span><span class=\"bp\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"n\">h2</span><span class=\"bp\">&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">Widget.savePanelWidgetInfo</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">hash</span> <span class=\"n\">HtmlDisplayPanel.javascript</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">return</span> <span class=\"n\">json</span><span class=\"bp\">%</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span> <span class=\"n\">html</span><span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"bp\">$</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">←</span> <span class=\"n\">Server.RpcEncodable.rpcEncode</span> <span class=\"n\">ht</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">})</span> <span class=\"n\">stx</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">Elab.